<li id="cite_note-31"><b><a href="#cite_ref-31" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" class="external autonumber" title="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
