<li id="cite_note-33"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" class="external autonumber" title="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" rel="nofollow">[4]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" class="external autonumber" title="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" rel="nofollow">[5]</a></li>
