<li id="cite_note-36"><b><a href="#cite_ref-36" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" class="external autonumber" title="http://theologyandsteak.wordpress.com/2007/10/23/book-review-the-shape-of-sola-scriptura-by-keith-a-mathison/" rel="nofollow">[7]</a></li>
