</div>
<p><a name="See_also" id="See_also"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sola_scriptura&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">See also</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bibliolatry" title="Bibliolatry">Bibliolatry</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ex_cathedra" title="Ex cathedra" class="mw-redirect">Ex cathedra</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ijtihad" title="Ijtihad">Ijtihad</a>, the Islamic concept of interpretation of religion and law not limited by tradition</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Qur%27an_alone" title="Qur'an alone">Qur'an alone</a>, an Islamic movement influenced in its theory by <i>sola scriptura</i>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wesleyan_Quadrilateral" title="Wesleyan Quadrilateral">Wesleyan Quadrilateral</a></li>
</ul>
