<li><a href="http://thirdmill.org/newfiles/kei_mathison/kei_mathison.critiquesolascriptura.html" class="external text" title="http://thirdmill.org/newfiles/kei_mathison/kei_mathison.critiquesolascriptura.html" rel="nofollow">"A Critique of the Evangelical Doctrine of Sola Scriptura"</a>, an excerpt from <i>The Shape of Sola Scriptura</i> (2001) by Keith Mathison (himself a Calvinistic evangelical)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.reformed.org/webfiles/antithesis/v1n5/ant_v1n5_issue.html" class="external text" title="http://www.reformed.org/webfiles/antithesis/v1n5/ant_v1n5_issue.html" rel="nofollow">A written debate on <i>Sola scriptura</i></a> between Douglas Jones and Gerald Matatics from <i>Antithesis Magazine</i></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bringyou.to/apologetics/a60.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.bringyou.to/apologetics/a60.htm" rel="nofollow">A formal written debate on <i>Sola scriptura</i></a> between Julie Staples and Apolonio Latar</li>
<li><a href="http://www.geocities.com/thecatholicconvert/solascriptura21.html" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/thecatholicconvert/solascriptura21.html" rel="nofollow">A Catholic assessment of <i>Sola scriptura</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.orthodoxinfo.com/inquirers/tca_solascriptura.aspx" class="external text" title="http://www.orthodoxinfo.com/inquirers/tca_solascriptura.aspx" rel="nofollow">An Orthodox Christian assessment of <i>Sola scriptura</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://pages.prodigy.net/frjohnwhiteford/responses_sola.htm" class="external text" title="http://pages.prodigy.net/frjohnwhiteford/responses_sola.htm" rel="nofollow">Orthodox Christian Responses to Protestant Apologists on <i>Sola Scriptura</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.catholicapologetics.org/ap040100.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.catholicapologetics.org/ap040100.htm" rel="nofollow">"Paradosis: The Handing On of Divine Revelation"</a> from a Catholic perspective</li>
</ul>


